summary: This is my version of the Dishonored trailer, in Skyrim :)
descriptionHtml:
I thought I might take a break from modding for a couple of days, so I made this trailer about the new upcoming Dishonored game. Song is used from the Dishonored trailer and I had a very fun time in making it. I\'ll put up a youtube link for you all to see, please comment here on the nexus, or on youtube if you like it :)

http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jYxFDCAH6Nk&feature=plcp
author: Passet
